========,1,preface.
Takotna ("Tocho’no’" in Upper Kuskokwim) is a census-designated place (CDP) in the Yukon-Koyukuk Census Area, Alaska, United States.
The population was 52 as of the 2010 Census, an increase of % from 50 at the 2000 Census.
========,2,Geography.
According to the 2010 Census, Mulberry is located at (62.982342, -156.084059).
